            published by UK-based independent games studio Ndemic Creations. The player
            creates and evolves a pathogen in an effort to destroy the world with a deadly
            plague. The game uses an epidemic model with a complex and realistic set of
            variables to simulate the spread and severity of the plague.
          </p>
          <p>

